Pattern Compliance

7. /check-patterns - Verify code follows
all patterns
- Multi-tenant isolation check
- Server action security
- PageContainer usage
- Navigation config
- Generates compliance report
8. /check-security - Security audit
- Rate limiting present
- Authentication checks
- Input validation
- No secrets in code
- OWASP top 10
9. /check-multi-tenant - Multi-tenant
safety audit
- All queries filter organizationId
- No cross-tenant leakage
- Fingerprinting correct
- Data scoping verified

17. /clean - Clean unused code
- Finds unused imports
- Detects dead code
- Removes old files
- Updates dependencies
